<div class="nha-container"><div class="nha-row"><div class="nha-gr-12 nha-gr-6@md nha-push-6@md"><div class="nha-large-story-spotlight-content">
<div class="nha-tag">Teacher</div><h2 class="nha-section-heading">Employee Spotlight: Music Class at DEA is Rock’n</h2>
